text: Ausma Kantāne-Ziedone (10 November 1941 – 29 May 2022) was a Latvian actress and politician. She was born in Riga, Latvia. She was a member of the Saeima from 2002 until 2010. She was part of the New Era Party. Kantāne-Ziedone died on 29 May 2022 in Riga at the age of 80. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Latvian politicians Category:Latvian movie actors
